@doc "## `vlfilter` in `vltransform()`\nOne of :\n\n- **case #1**\n  - `timeUnit` :   (one of yearquarter,utcyear,utcminutes,day,utcmilliseconds,month,hoursminutes,quarter,utcmonthdate,quartermonth,utchoursminutes,utcyearquarter,yearmonthdate,hoursminutesseconds,year,utcquartermonth,date,hours,utcseconds,utcdate,yearmonth,utcquarter,utcyearmonthdate,utchoursminutesseconds,utchours,utcyearmonthdatehoursminutes,utcminutesseconds,minutes,utcyearmonthdatehours,utcyearmonth,utcday,utcmonth,seconds,yearquartermonth,yearmonthdatehours,monthdate,utcyearmonthdatehoursminutesseconds,utcsecondsmilliseconds,milliseconds,yearmonthdatehoursminutesseconds,yearmonthdatehoursminutes,secondsmilliseconds,minutesseconds,utcyearquartermonth)\n  - `equal` : The value that the field should be equal to. *see help for `vlequal()`*\n  - `field` : Field to be filtered. *see help for `vlfield()`*\n\n- **case #2**\n  - `selection` : Filter using a selection name. *see help for `vlselection()`*\n\n- **case #3**\n  - `timeUnit` :   (one of yearquarter,utcyear,utcminutes,day,utcmilliseconds,month,hoursminutes,quarter,utcmonthdate,quartermonth,utchoursminutes,utcyearquarter,yearmonthdate,hoursminutesseconds,year,utcquartermonth,date,hours,utcseconds,utcdate,yearmonth,utcquarter,utcyearmonthdate,utchoursminutesseconds,utchours,utcyearmonthdatehoursminutes,utcminutesseconds,minutes,utcyearmonthdatehours,utcyearmonth,utcday,utcmonth,seconds,yearquartermonth,yearmonthdatehours,monthdate,utcyearmonthdatehoursminutesseconds,utcsecondsmilliseconds,milliseconds,yearmonthdatehoursminutesseconds,yearmonthdatehoursminutes,secondsmilliseconds,minutesseconds,utcyearquartermonth)\n  - `field` : Field to be filtered *see help for `vlfield()`*\n  - `oneOf` : A set of values that the `field`'s value should be a member of, for a data item included in the filtered data. *see help for `vloneOf()`*\n\n- **case #4**\n  - `range` : An array of inclusive minimum and maximum values for a field value of a data item to be included in the filtered data. *see help for `vlrange()`*\n  - `timeUnit` :   (one of yearquarter,utcyear,utcminutes,day,utcmilliseconds,month,hoursminutes,quarter,utcmonthdate,quartermonth,utchoursminutes,utcyearquarter,yearmonthdate,hoursminutesseconds,year,utcquartermonth,date,hours,utcseconds,utcdate,yearmonth,utcquarter,utcyearmonthdate,utchoursminutesseconds,utchours,utcyearmonthdatehoursminutes,utcminutesseconds,minutes,utcyearmonthdatehours,utcyearmonth,utcday,utcmonth,seconds,yearquartermonth,yearmonthdatehours,monthdate,utcyearmonthdatehoursminutesseconds,utcsecondsmilliseconds,milliseconds,yearmonthdatehoursminutesseconds,yearmonthdatehoursminutes,secondsmilliseconds,minutesseconds,utcyearquartermonth)\n  - `field` : Field to be filtered *see help for `vlfield()`*\n" vlfilter
@doc "## `vlselection` in `plot()`\nA key-value mapping between selection names and definitions.\n\n\n## `vlselection` in `vllayer()`, `vlhconcat()`, `vlspec()` and `vlvconcat()`\nA key-value mapping between selection names and definitions.\n\n\n## `vlselection` in `vlconfig()`\n- `interval` :  *see help for `vlinterval()`*\n- `multi` :   - `translate` :   (String/Symbol or Bool)\n  - `nearest` :   (Bool)\n  - `fields` :   (Array of String/Symbol)\n  - `bind` :  *see help for `vlbind()`*\n  - `on` :   (Any)\n  - `encodings` :   (Array of String/Symbol)\n  - `zoom` :   (String/Symbol or Bool)\n  - `resolve` :  *see help for `vlresolve()`*\n  - `toggle` :   (String/Symbol or Bool)\n- `single` :   - `translate` :   (String/Symbol or Bool)\n  - `nearest` :   (Bool)\n  - `fields` :   (Array of String/Symbol)\n  - `bind` :  *see help for `vlbind()`*\n  - `on` :   (Any)\n  - `encodings` :   (Array of String/Symbol)\n  - `zoom` :   (String/Symbol or Bool)\n  - `resolve` :  *see help for `vlresolve()`*\n  - `toggle` :   (String/Symbol or Bool)\n" vlselection
